data.description: Beautiful Corner unit with Panoramic LAKE VIEWS the minute you walk in through the front door that takes your breath away. 2 Bedroom with Loft/ 3rd Bedroom option very easily converted to a 3rd bedroom, has window. Tiled flooring downstairs and wood floors on staircase and all upstairs.  NO carpet.  A/C is only 4 years old, and Stove was also replaced 4 years ago.  Very well maintained.  Complete Accordion Shutters throughout.Great opportunity for a first-time home buyer, investor or anyone downsizing.  Located in the unique sought-after community of Smithbrooke.
